{"tid":1541424,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我今晚真係喊左出黎","createTime":"2019-09-04T14:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:46:19.000Z","uid":42687,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb963dcc0fb73dcc24e76fba6279a424428a470b","tid":1541424,"uid":42687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"話說我開左個餐飲招聘谷，入面有百幾人，由於而家時勢唔好，我就叫大家唔好係谷到講野。每一日我都會搵唔同既炒散工POST出去，佢地有興趣既就自己去見工。<br />\n由於冇人講野，所以每一日我都係自己出POST，咁岩個日出去行我就會講聲我出去喇今日冇招聘等等。我從來都冉唔知有冇人睇我POST既野,或者有冇人因為呢個谷而見得成工。有時我會諗都唔知有冇用，幫唔幫到Ｄ有需要既人。<br />\n終於到今晚有人出聲要幫手，需要一份炒散，因為個身得幾十蚊，我個下真係喊左出黎，我唔知你係咩人，但點解我地既社會要令後生仔得返幾十蚊係身飯都冇得開，我喊到收唔到聲，而我可以做既只係得咁少，就係比一份好少錢既工佢地。<br />\n對唔住for 1999，我希望以後我都係自說自話冇人睇我出既招聘，你地個個都唔再需要去炒散，學生返去讀書，後生仔繼續去溝仔溝女,大人繼續返工..."},{"pid":"c389e620d51a8e79f0075452cb892529910edc2b","tid":1541424,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: 